<a name="sub27969_10_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="戏曲" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="10-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3   MARK_MODULE" data-index="10_1" data-uuid="godp6zztg4" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>戏曲</h3>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq56s3om" ><a class="
				lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206 J-lemma-album
							"
            data-album-id="4497275813"
			title="庐剧"  href="/pic/%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E7%9C%81/526353/4497275813/8718367adab44aed26668d06b21c8701a18bfb23?fr=lemma&fromModule=lemma_content-image&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:222px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:146.4px;">
<img class="picture" alt="庐剧" src="https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/8718367adab44aed26668d06b21c8701a18bfb23?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_220,limit_1" style="width:220px;height:146.4px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
庐剧<span class="number">(9张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg" style="width:220px;">
</div>
</a>安徽省被称为中国戏曲之乡，安徽戏剧表演艺术历史悠久，品种较多，名家迭出。地方戏种现存30余种，分别有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E6%A2%85%E6%88%8F/2677" data-lemmaid="2677">黄梅戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E5%89%A7/885777" data-lemmaid="885777">徽剧</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BA%90%E5%89%A7/886312" data-lemmaid="886312">庐剧</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B3%97%E5%B7%9E%E6%88%8F/10037231" data-lemmaid="10037231">泗州戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%9D%A0%E5%AD%90%E6%88%8F/6381507" data-lemmaid="6381507">坠子戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8A%B1%E9%BC%93%E7%81%AF/5109378" data-lemmaid="5109378">花鼓灯</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%8E%A8%E5%89%A7/850865" data-lemmaid="850865">推剧</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%97%A8%E5%AD%90%E6%88%8F/7165714" data-lemmaid="7165714">嗨子戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%87%E5%8D%97%E8%AF%8D/8346608" data-lemmaid="8346608">文南词</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9B%AE%E8%BF%9E%E6%88%8F/9125024" data-lemmaid="9125024">目连戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%90%AB%E5%BC%93%E6%88%8F/3343245" data-lemmaid="3343245">含弓戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B3%E8%B0%83/1637464" data-lemmaid="1637464">四平调</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B4%AA%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%8F/10781498" data-lemmaid="10781498">洪山戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%AA%E6%B9%96%E6%9B%B2%E5%AD%90%E6%88%8F/1454440" data-lemmaid="1454440">太湖曲子戏</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%80%80%E8%85%94/22330900" data-lemmaid="22330900">怀腔</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BC%B9%E8%85%94/5850490" data-lemmaid="5850490">弹腔</a>等等。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="29" data-ctrmap=":29,">
[29]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_29_27969" id="ref_29_27969">&nbsp;</a>
黄梅戏，旧称<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E6%A2%85%E8%B0%83/7871728" data-lemmaid="7871728">黄梅调</a>或<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%87%87%E8%8C%B6%E6%88%8F/468358" data-lemmaid="468358">采茶戏</a>，是<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%8F%E6%9B%B2%E5%89%A7%E7%A7%8D/13003206" data-lemmaid="13003206">中国五大戏曲剧种</a>之一。<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E5%89%A7/885777" data-lemmaid="885777">徽剧</a>是京剧的主要源流之一，池州的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%82%A9%E6%88%8F/828672" data-lemmaid="828672">傩戏</a>号称“戏剧活化石”，淮河两岸流行的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8A%B1%E9%BC%93%E7%81%AF/5109378" data-lemmaid="5109378">花鼓灯</a>被誉为“东方芭蕾”。</div><div class="anchor-list  MARK_MODULE">
<a name="10_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_10_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="文学" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="10-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3   MARK_MODULE" data-index="10_2" data-uuid="godp89ufut" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>文学</h3>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpagtq1o" ><a class="
				lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206 J-lemma-album
							"
            data-album-id="4497275817"
			title="徽文化建筑"  href="/pic/%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E7%9C%81/526353/4497275817/f2deb48f8c5494eef083a8a82ff5e0fe98257ed9?fr=lemma&fromModule=lemma_content-image&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:222px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:150.33333333333px;">
<img class="picture" alt="徽文化建筑" src="https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/f2deb48f8c5494eef083a8a82ff5e0fe98257ed9?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_220,limit_1" style="width:220px;height:150.33333333333px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
徽文化建筑<span class="number">(2张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg" style="width:220px;">
</div>
</a>安徽省古代代表文学是<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96/1610731" data-lemmaid="1610731">徽文化</a><b>、</b><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%89%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/886190" data-lemmaid="886190">新安理学</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96/4715812" data-lemmaid="4715812">道教文化</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/75356" data-lemmaid="75356">理学</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%A1%90%E5%9F%8E%E6%B4%BE/294837" data-lemmaid="294837">桐城派</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%89%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6/815180" data-lemmaid="815180">建安文学</a>，桐城派文论体系和古文运动的形成，始于<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B9%E8%8B%9E/78796" data-lemmaid="78796">方苞</a>，经<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%88%98%E5%A4%A7%E6%AB%86/838041" data-lemmaid="838041">刘大櫆</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A7%9A%E9%BC%90/381326" data-lemmaid="381326">姚鼐</a>而发展成为一个声势显赫的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6%E6%B5%81%E6%B4%BE/2455788" data-lemmaid="2455788">文学流派</a>。新安理学是中国思想史上曾起过重大影响的学派，其奠基人<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A8%8B%E9%A2%A2/1453707" data-lemmaid="1453707">程颢</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A8%8B%E9%A2%90/1453531" data-lemmaid="1453531">程颐</a>及集大成者<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9C%B1%E7%86%B9/106669" data-lemmaid="106669">朱熹</a>，祖籍均在安徽新安江畔。朱熹亦自称“新安朱熹”。理学的奠基人洛阳程颢、程颐和集大成婺源朱熹的祖籍均在安徽<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AD%99%E5%8E%BF/645326" data-lemmaid="645326">歙县</a>篁墩，故誉为“<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A8%8B%E6%9C%B1%E9%98%99%E9%87%8C/7059487" data-lemmaid="7059487">程朱阙里</a>”。</div><div class="anchor-list  MARK_MODULE">
<a name="10_3" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_10_3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="美术" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="10-3" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3   MARK_MODULE" data-index="10_3" data-uuid="godp89ufy6" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>美术</h3>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq56s3qn" ><a class="
				lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206 J-lemma-album
							"
            data-album-id="4497275814"
			title="新安画派"  href="/pic/%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E7%9C%81/526353/4497275814/3812b31bb051f819e0e69510d8b44aed2f73e7ad?fr=lemma&fromModule=lemma_content-image&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:222px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:136.95px;">
<img class="picture" alt="新安画派" src="https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/3812b31bb051f819e0e69510d8b44aed2f73e7ad?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_220,limit_1" style="width:220px;height:136.95px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
新安画派<span class="number">(7张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg" style="width:220px;">
</div>
</a>安徽省历史上有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%89%E7%94%BB%E6%B4%BE/886451" data-lemmaid="886451">新安画派</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BE%99%E5%9F%8E%E7%94%BB%E6%B4%BE/1217787" data-lemmaid="1217787">龙城画派</a>，版画流派有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8A%9C%E6%B9%96%E9%93%81%E7%94%BB/1439456" data-lemmaid="1439456">芜湖铁画</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E6%B4%BE%E7%89%88%E7%94%BB/886008" data-lemmaid="886008">徽派版画</a>等。新安画派画派先驱程家燧、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B0%B8%E6%98%8C/150088" data-lemmaid="150088">李永昌</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E6%B5%81%E8%8A%B3/4212614" data-lemmaid="4212614">李流芳</a>，鼎盛时期主要成员有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E7%8E%89/3616228" data-lemmaid="3616228">方式玉</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%8A%E7%B4%A0/3766545" data-lemmaid="3766545">王尊素</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%90%B4%E5%B1%B1%E6%B6%9B/5159782" data-lemmaid="5159782">吴山涛</a>、王家珍、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%88%B4%E6%9C%AC%E5%AD%9D/2585165" data-lemmaid="2585165">戴本孝</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%90%B4%E9%BE%99/6837476" data-lemmaid="6837476">吴龙</a>、吴田标、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%9B%AA%E5%BA%84/8827438" data-lemmaid="8827438">雪庄</a>等，新安画派在中国绘画史上具有重要地位。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="30-31" data-ctrmap=":30,:31,">
[30-31]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_30_27969" id="ref_30_27969">&nbsp;</a><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_31_27969" id="ref_31_27969">&nbsp;</a></div><div class="anchor-list  MARK_MODULE">
<a name="10_4" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_10_4" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="方言" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="10-4" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3   MARK_MODULE" data-index="10_4" data-uuid="godp6xnkn0" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>方言</h3>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzvkg" ><i>主词条：</i><i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%80/1971032" data-lemmaid="1971032">安徽方言</a></i></div><table log-set-param="table_view" data-sort="sortDisabled" data-id="godp6xnkop"><caption>安徽境内方言</caption><tr data-id="godp6xnkrc"><th align="center" width="116" data-id="godp6xnksw"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6xnkvm" ><b>类别</b></div></th><th align="center" width="675" data-id="godp6xnkxe"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6xnkzu" ><b>分布</b></div></th></tr><tr data-id="godp6xnl1i"><td align="center" width="116" data-id="godp6xnl3d"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzyq4" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E8%AF%AD/4643230" data-lemmaid="4643230">徽语</a></div></td><td width="675" data-id="godp6xnl7u"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzyyf" >皖南徽语<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E8%AF%AD/4643230" data-lemmaid="4643230">徽语</a>是现代汉语中新近被确定的十大<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%80%E5%8C%BA/8116933" data-lemmaid="8116933">方言区</a>之一（也有专家认为是吴语的分支）。皖南徽语主要指旧<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E5%B7%9E%E5%BA%9C/9311561" data-lemmaid="9311561">徽州府</a>及部分毗邻地区的方言。<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AD%99%E5%8E%BF/645326" data-lemmaid="645326">歙县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BB%A9%E6%BA%AA/10950005" data-lemmaid="10950005">绩溪</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%97%8C%E5%BE%B7/1504768" data-lemmaid="1504768">旌德</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B1%AF%E6%BA%AA/2840659" data-lemmaid="2840659">屯溪</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BC%91%E5%AE%81/6353887" data-lemmaid="6353887">休宁</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%9F%E5%8E%BF/5294317" data-lemmaid="5294317">黟县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A5%81%E9%97%A8/10753994" data-lemmaid="10753994">祁门</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%81%E5%9B%BD/1660495" data-lemmaid="1660495">宁国</a>（南鸿门乡等地）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%9C%E8%87%B3%E5%8E%BF/8344508" data-lemmaid="8344508">东至县</a>（东南部木塔一带）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9F%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%8E%BF/4352103" data-lemmaid="4352103">石台县</a>（占大区）等地的方言。</div></td></tr><tr data-id="godp6xnleo"><td align="center" width="116" height="50" data-id="godp6xnlgj"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzyg6" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%90%B4%E8%AF%AD/659462" data-lemmaid="659462">吴语</a></div></td><td width="675" height="50" data-id="godp6xnlko"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzymu" >吴语是现代汉语的十大方言之一。安徽省的吴语主要分布在黄山山脉以北和以东的14个县市范围内。其中<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E5%8E%BF/43490" data-lemmaid="43490">太平县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B3%BE%E5%8E%BF/3303382" data-lemmaid="3303382">泾县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9F%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%8E%BF/4352103" data-lemmaid="4352103">石台县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%93%9C%E9%99%B5/1538653" data-lemmaid="1538653">铜陵</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%B9%81%E6%98%8C/2068507" data-lemmaid="2068507">繁昌</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8D%97%E9%99%B5/7773247" data-lemmaid="7773247">南陵</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B9%BE%E6%B2%9A%E5%8C%BA/22671815" data-lemmaid="22671815">湾沚区</a>等地吴语的通用面较广。</div></td></tr><tr data-id="godp6xnlqg"><td align="center" width="116" data-id="godp6xnlsb"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzy5u" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%B5%A3%E8%AF%AD/1322722" data-lemmaid="1322722">赣语</a></div></td><td width="675" data-id="godp6xnlvi"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzycs" >安徽省的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%B5%A3%E8%AF%AD/1322722" data-lemmaid="1322722">赣语</a>主要指通用于皖西南<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%B1%B1/709010" data-lemmaid="709010">大别山</a>南麓和沿江两岸的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%89%E5%BA%86%E5%B8%82/211620" data-lemmaid="211620">安庆市</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B2%B3%E8%A5%BF/5676929" data-lemmaid="5676929">岳西</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%BD%9C%E5%B1%B1/6623606" data-lemmaid="6623606">潜山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%AA%E6%B9%96/18725803" data-lemmaid="18725803">太湖</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%BF%E6%9D%BE/7168585" data-lemmaid="7168585">宿松</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9C%9B%E6%B1%9F/727398" data-lemmaid="727398">望江</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%80%80%E5%AE%81/2613318" data-lemmaid="2613318">怀宁</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%9C%E8%87%B3%E5%8E%BF/8344508" data-lemmaid="8344508">东至县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%B4%B5%E6%B1%A0%E5%B8%82/4879257" data-lemmaid="4879257">贵池市</a>西部及东南角等8个市县的方言。当地人传说，他们的祖先大概是在明初由江西的“瓦西坝”成批迁徙此地定居的。</div></td></tr><tr data-id="godp6xnm1f"><td align="center" width="116" data-id="godp6xnm3b"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6xnm5r" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B7%AE%E5%AE%98%E8%AF%9D/450260" data-lemmaid="450260">江淮官话</a></div></td><td width="675" data-id="godp6xnm7l"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpiissa2" >安徽省的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B7%AE%E5%AE%98%E8%AF%9D/450260" data-lemmaid="450260">江淮官话</a>区，包括长江以南的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B1%A0%E5%B7%9E/992847" data-lemmaid="992847">池州</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%93%9C%E9%99%B5/1538653" data-lemmaid="1538653">铜陵</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8A%9C%E6%B9%96/222481" data-lemmaid="222481">芜湖</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%A3%E5%9F%8E/1132736" data-lemmaid="1132736">宣城</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A9%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1/13144" data-lemmaid="13144">马鞍山</a>等11个市县，和淮河以北的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%80%80%E8%BF%9C%E5%8E%BF/26180" data-lemmaid="26180">怀远县</a>，江淮之间的合肥（除<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%95%BF%E4%B8%B0%E5%8E%BF/10057708" data-lemmaid="10057708">长丰县</a>北部）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%BB%81%E5%B7%9E/1131131" data-lemmaid="1131131">滁州</a>（除<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%98%8E%E5%85%89/1134655" data-lemmaid="1134655">明光</a>部分地区、凤阳县）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%AD%E5%AE%89%E5%B8%82/211125" data-lemmaid="211125">六安市</a>（除<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%9C%8D%E9%82%B1/228195" data-lemmaid="228195">霍邱</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AF%BF%E5%8E%BF/192372" data-lemmaid="192372">寿县</a>北部、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%87%91%E5%AF%A8%E5%8E%BF/1284652" data-lemmaid="1284652">金寨县</a>西北部）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B7%AE%E5%8D%97/197644" data-lemmaid="197644">淮南</a>（限东部九龙岗、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%8A%E7%AA%91/54502083" data-lemmaid="54502083">上窑</a>、洛河等地）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%89%E5%BA%86/350307" data-lemmaid="350307">安庆</a>（除<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9C%9B%E6%B1%9F%E5%8E%BF/8340294" data-lemmaid="8340294">望江县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%80%80%E5%AE%81%E5%8E%BF/807351" data-lemmaid="807351">怀宁县</a>等赣语地区）等县市。</div></td></tr><tr data-id="godp6xnme4"><td align="center" width="116" data-id="godp6xnmfy"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6xnmie" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%98%E8%AF%9D/1115854" data-lemmaid="1115854">中原官话</a></div></td><td width="675" data-id="godp6xnmk6"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godp6zzxrf" >安徽省淮河以北的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B7%AE%E5%8C%97/3973540" data-lemmaid="3973540">淮北</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%BF%E5%B7%9E/954010" data-lemmaid="954010">宿州</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%98%9C%E9%98%B3/439805" data-lemmaid="439805">阜阳</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%B3%E5%B7%9E/146796" data-lemmaid="146796">亳州</a>和沿淮以南的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%87%A4%E9%98%B3%E5%8E%BF/5285002" data-lemmaid="5285002">凤阳县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%9A%8C%E5%9F%A0/193105" data-lemmaid="193105">蚌埠</a>（不含<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%80%80%E8%BF%9C%E5%8E%BF/26180" data-lemmaid="26180">怀远县</a>南部）、淮南（不含东部九龙岗、上窑、洛河等地区）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AF%BF%E5%8E%BF/192372" data-lemmaid="192372">寿县</a>（北部）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%9C%8D%E9%82%B1/228195" data-lemmaid="228195">霍邱</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%87%91%E5%AF%A8%E5%8E%BF/1284652" data-lemmaid="1284652">金寨县</a>（西北部）、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%95%BF%E4%B8%B0%E5%8E%BF/10057708" data-lemmaid="10057708">长丰县</a>（北部）等市县的话，均属中原官话。</div></td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list  MARK_MODULE">
<a name="10_5" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_10_5" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="地名" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="10-5" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3   MARK_MODULE" data-index="10_5" data-uuid="godq2f830k" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>地名</h3>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq56q5mb" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B9%BE%E9%9A%86/129924" data-lemmaid="129924">乾隆</a>年间，《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B8%85%E4%BC%9A%E5%85%B8/7304603" data-lemmaid="7304603">清会典</a>》从法律层面确定了<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A1%BA%E6%B2%BB/301130" data-lemmaid="301130">顺治</a>末、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BA%B7%E7%86%99/130006" data-lemmaid="130006">康熙</a>初江南等三省分省的结果，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B9%BE%E9%9A%86/129924" data-lemmaid="129924">乾隆</a>《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B8%85%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%9F%E5%BF%97/5261784" data-lemmaid="5261784">清一统志</a>》将江苏与安徽两省分开，目录中已经全部为“以上某某省”。省名取当时安庆、徽州两府首字合成，因境内有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9A%96%E5%B1%B1/7434924" data-lemmaid="7434924">皖山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%98%A5%E7%A7%8B/982807" data-lemmaid="982807">春秋</a>时期有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8F%A4%E7%9A%96%E5%9B%BD/5954397" data-lemmaid="5954397">古皖国</a>而简称皖。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="11" data-ctrmap=":11,">
[11]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_11_27969" id="ref_11_27969">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list  MARK_MODULE">
<a name="11" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_11" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="风景名胜" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2  J-chapter " data-index="11" data-uuid="godq1l4e7l" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>风景名胜</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="11" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="audio-play part-audio-play J-part-audio-play" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_voice-play"></em>
<span class="J-part-audio-text">播报</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list  MARK_MODULE">
<a name="11_1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_11_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="概述" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="11-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3   MARK_MODULE" data-index="11_1" data-uuid="tx5S4OlBMjVi" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>概述</h3>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq56s4kg" ><div class="lemma-picture J-lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" 
	 
		style="width:220px; float: right;"
	>
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E7%9C%81/526353/0/c9fcc3cec3fdfc03d766afecda3f8794a4c22643?fr=lemma&fromModule=lemma_content-image&ct=single" target="_blank"
			title="亳州谯望楼" 
	 
		style="width:220px;height:95.612298071912px;"
		>
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/c9fcc3cec3fdfc03d766afecda3f8794a4c22643?x-bce-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_440,limit_1"  alt="亳州谯望楼"
							style="width:220px;height:95.612298071912px;"
					/>
</a>
<span class="description">
亳州谯望楼
</span>
</div>截至2017年11月，安徽省拥有1处<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E5%8F%8C%E9%87%8D%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7/10543306" data-lemmaid="10543306">世界文化与自然双重遗产</a>，2处<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E9%81%97%E4%BA%A7/290153" data-lemmaid="290153">世界文化遗产</a>，2处<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD/3604728" data-lemmaid="3604728">世界地质公园</a>，5座<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%90%8D%E5%9F%8E/6412721" data-lemmaid="6412721">国家历史文化名城</a>（<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AD%99%E5%8E%BF/645326" data-lemmaid="645326">歙县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AF%BF%E5%8E%BF/192372" data-lemmaid="192372">寿县</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%B3%E5%B7%9E/146796" data-lemmaid="146796">亳州</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%89%E5%BA%86/350307" data-lemmaid="350307">安庆</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BB%A9%E6%BA%AA/10950005" data-lemmaid="10950005">绩溪</a>），6个<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%BA%A7%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%8C%BA/7516695" data-lemmaid="7516695">国家级自然保护区</a>，9家<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E6%B9%BF%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD/6910557" data-lemmaid="6910557">国家湿地公园</a>，12处国家级重点风景名胜区（<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E5%B1%B1/9416" data-lemmaid="9416">黄山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B9%9D%E5%8D%8E%E5%B1%B1/7008" data-lemmaid="7008">九华山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A9%E6%9F%B1%E5%B1%B1/1770" data-lemmaid="1770">天柱山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%90%85%E7%90%8A%E5%B1%B1/258812" data-lemmaid="258812">琅琊山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BD%90%E4%BA%91%E5%B1%B1/5184" data-lemmaid="5184">齐云山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%87%87%E7%9F%B3%E7%9F%B6/257090" data-lemmaid="257090">采石矶</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B7%A2%E6%B9%96/19914782" data-lemmaid="19914782">巢湖</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8A%B1%E5%B1%B1%E8%B0%9C%E7%AA%9F/5286508" data-lemmaid="5286508">花山谜窟</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%AA%E6%9E%81%E6%B4%9E/257273" data-lemmaid="257273">太极洞</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8A%B1%E4%BA%AD%E6%B9%96/637232" data-lemmaid="637232">花亭湖</a>），11处国家地质公园，30个国家级森林公园，130处<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E9%87%8D%E7%82%B9%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D/2960685" data-lemmaid="2960685">全国重点文物保护单位</a>，708处省保单位，3161处市县保单位。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="32-35" data-ctrmap=":32,:33,:34,:35,">
[32-35]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_32_27969" id="ref_32_27969">&nbsp;</a><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_33_27969" id="ref_33_27969">&nbsp;</a><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_34_27969" id="ref_34_27969">&nbsp;</a><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_35_27969" id="ref_35_27969">&nbsp;</a></div><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq6jjwex" >截至2021年02月26日，安徽省A级旅游景区总数625家，其中5A级景区12家；安徽省旅游生产经营单位有3.3万个，其中“全国旅游集团20强”3家；旅行社达1519家，星级饭店302家。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="36" data-ctrmap="2I7nezNUowK:36,">
[36]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_36_27969" id="ref_36_27969">&nbsp;</a>
</div><table log-set-param="table_view" data-sort="sortDisabled" data-id="godpbutz86"><caption>安徽省十六座城市的代表性旅游资源</caption><tr data-id="godpbutzaz"><td align="center" width="418" data-id="godpbutzd0"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpbwarxx" >合肥的三国胜迹</div></td><td align="center" width="373" data-id="godpbutzh0"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpbwas0u" >宿州的楚风汉韵</div></td></tr><tr data-id="godpbutzlk"><td align="center" width="418" data-id="godpbutznj"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpbutzq5" >芜湖的滨江湖影</div></td><td align="center" width="373" data-id="godpbutzs0"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpbutzun" >淮南的八公山</div></td></tr><tr >池州的佛教圣地</div></td></tr><tr data-id="godpbuu1d0"><td align="center" width="418" data-id="godpbuu1ex"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpbuu1hf" >铜陵的铜都风光</div></td><td <div class="description">
安徽旅游 美好安徽欢迎您<span class="number">(17张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg" style="width:220px;">
</div>
</a>安徽省山多秀丽，且负盛名，其中有黄山市的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E5%B1%B1/9416" data-lemmaid="9416">黄山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BD%90%E4%BA%91%E5%B1%B1/5184" data-lemmaid="5184">齐云山</a>，合肥的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A7%E8%9C%80%E5%B1%B1/816195" data-lemmaid="816195">大蜀山</a>、宣城的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%95%AC%E4%BA%AD%E5%B1%B1/3295589" data-lemmaid="3295589">敬亭山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9F%8F%E6%9E%A7%E5%B1%B1/10979524" data-lemmaid="10979524">柏枧山</a>，池州的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B9%9D%E5%8D%8E%E5%B1%B1/7008" data-lemmaid="7008">九华山</a>，淮南的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%B1/199006" data-lemmaid="199006">八公山</a>，芜湖的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%B5%AD%E5%B1%B1/7695672" data-lemmaid="7695672">赭山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%AB%E5%B1%B1/8407197" data-lemmaid="8407197">丫山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A9%AC%E4%BB%81%E5%A5%87%E5%B3%B0/6725377" data-lemmaid="6725377">马仁奇峰</a>，滁州的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%90%85%E7%90%8A%E5%B1%B1/258812" data-lemmaid="258812">琅琊山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9A%87%E7%94%AB%E5%B1%B1/4658162" data-lemmaid="4658162">皇甫山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%9F%AD%E5%B1%B1/8502993" data-lemmaid="8502993">韭山</a>，宿州的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9A%87%E8%97%8F%E5%B3%AA/1991193" data-lemmaid="1991193">皇藏峪</a>、突山，安庆的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A9%E6%9F%B1%E5%B1%B1/1770" data-lemmaid="1770">天柱山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A4%E5%B1%B1/47161" data-lemmaid="47161">小孤山</a>，铜陵的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%B1/24173" data-lemmaid="24173">浮山</a>，六安的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%87%E4%BD%9B%E5%B1%B1/7385957" data-lemmaid="7385957">万佛山</a>、大别山<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E5%AF%A8/2811226" data-lemmaid="2811226">天堂寨</a>，淮北的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9B%B8%E5%B1%B1/3023064" data-lemmaid="3023064">相山</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BE%99%E8%84%8A%E5%B1%B1/6066802" data-lemmaid="6066802">龙脊山</a>等。</div><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq56s5di" ><div class="lemma-picture J-lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" 
	 
		style="width:220px; float: right;"

<span class="description">
明中都
</span>
</div>安徽省的水兼江河湖，中国第一大河——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%95%BF%E6%B1%9F/388" data-lemmaid="388">长江</a>横穿东西，江面辽阔。中国五大淡水湖之一<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B7%A2%E6%B9%96/18045" data-lemmaid="18045">巢湖</a>，及被称为东方<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%97%A5%E5%86%85%E7%93%A6%E6%B9%96/242240" data-lemmaid="242240">日内瓦湖</a>——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B9%96/24167" data-lemmaid="24167">太平湖</a>，皖北第一大湖泊——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BE%99%E5%AD%90%E6%B9%96/46514" data-lemmaid="46514">龙子湖</a>。<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%BF%E5%B7%9E/954010" data-lemmaid="954010">宿州</a>的<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E6%B2%B3%E6%95%85%E9%81%93/19512349" data-lemmaid="19512349">黄河故道</a>是安徽的湿地旅游资源。安徽的名泉极多，有江南第一泉——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%9C%A3%E6%B3%89/5287146" data-lemmaid="5287146">圣泉</a>、天下第七泉——<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%99%BD%E4%B9%B3%E6%B3%89/2668857" data-lemmaid="2668857">白乳泉</a>。安徽主要古道有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E6%9D%AD%E5%8F%A4%E9%81%93/9695561" data-lemmaid="9695561">徽杭古道</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%97%8C%E6%AD%99%E5%8F%A4%E9%81%93/19420957" data-lemmaid="19420957">旌歙古道</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E5%AE%89%E5%8F%A4%E9%81%93/6207973" data-lemmaid="6207973">徽安古道</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%A4%E9%81%93/6221316" data-lemmaid="6221316">徽开古道</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E9%A5%B6%E5%8F%A4%E9%81%93/8601463" data-lemmaid="8601463">徽饶古道</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E9%9D%92%E5%8F%A4%E9%81%93/6221352" data-lemmaid="6221352">徽青古道</a>。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="37" data-ctrmap=":37,">
[37]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_37_27969" id="ref_37_27969">&nbsp;</a>

<a name="11_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_11_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="主要景区" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="11-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3   MARK_MODULE" data-index="11_2" data-uuid="godq1l4ff7" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>主要景区</h3>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" data-sort="sortDisabled" data-id="godp2tggh5"><caption>安徽境内国家5A级景区</caption><tr data-id="godponkxjt"><th align="center" width="115" data-id="godponkxlr"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godponkxod" ><b>所在地</b></div></th><th align="center" width="676" data-id="godponkxq5"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godponkxsk" ><b>景区</b></div></th></tr><tr data-id="godponkxu8"><td align="center" width="115" data-id="godponkxw2"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godponkxxr" >合肥</div></td><td align="center" width="676" data-id="godponkxzi"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godponky27" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%89%E6%B2%B3%E5%8F%A4%E9%95%87/5846288" data-lemmaid="5846288">三河古镇</a></div></td></tr><tr data-id="godponky3v"><td align="center" width="115" data-id="godponky5p"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godponky83" >黄山</div></td><td align="center" width="676" data-id="godponky9u"><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godpoov5ph" ><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E5%B1%B1%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%8C%BA/1350521" data-lemmaid="1350521">黄山风景区</a>、<a target=_blank <a name="名优特产" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2  J-chapter " data-index="12" data-uuid="godq13b57i" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>名优特产</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="12" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="audio-play part-audio-play J-part-audio-play" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_voice-play"></em>
<span class="J-part-audio-text">播报</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq13b59a" ><i>主词条：</i><i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E8%8F%9C/760635" data-lemmaid="760635">安徽菜</a></i><i>、</i><i><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%89%E5%BE%BD%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%B6/3555591" data-lemmaid="3555591">安徽茶叶</a></i></div><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq1ndld7" >安徽省饮食名目繁多，主要有<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E5%B7%9E%E8%8F%9C/17218790" data-lemmaid="17218790">徽州菜</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BA%90%E5%B7%9E%E8%8F%9C/19950332" data-lemmaid="19950332">庐州菜</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B2%BF%E6%B1%9F%E8%8F%9C/10148811" data-lemmaid="10148811">沿江菜</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B2%BF%E6%B7%AE%E8%8F%9C/10156777" data-lemmaid="10156777">沿淮菜</a>等，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%BD%E8%8F%9C/1139026" data-lemmaid="1139026">徽菜</a>为中国<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%AB%E5%A4%A7%E8%8F%9C%E7%B3%BB/873948" data-lemmaid="873948">八大菜系</a>之一。徽州菜起源于歙县，绩溪的徽帮厨师将它发扬光大。徽菜素以重油、重色、重火功，色香味形俱全而盛行于世。徽菜在烹调方法上擅长烧、炖、蒸。<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B2%BF%E6%B1%9F%E8%8F%9C/10148811" data-lemmaid="10148811">沿江菜</a>盛行于<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%8A%9C%E6%B9%96/222481" data-lemmaid="222481">芜湖</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%89%E5%BA%86/350307" data-lemmaid="350307">安庆</a>及<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B7%A2%E6%B9%96/18045" data-lemmaid="18045">巢湖</a>地区，它以烹调河鲜、家禽见长。沿淮菜主要由<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%9A%8C%E5%9F%A0/193105" data-lemmaid="193105">蚌埠</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AE%BF%E5%B7%9E/954010" data-lemmaid="954010">宿州</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%98%9C%E9%98%B3/439805" data-lemmaid="439805">阜阳</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B7%AE%E5%8C%97/3973540" data-lemmaid="3973540">淮北</a>等地地方风味构成，菜品讲究咸中带辣，汤汁味重色浓，并习惯用香菜佐味和配色。</div><table log-set-param="table_view" </div><div class="para-title level-2  J-chapter " data-index="13" data-uuid="godq0s6208" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>著名人物</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="13" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>

<span class="J-part-audio-text">播报</span>
</a>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" data-sort="sortDisabled" data-id="godp2thj8w"><caption>安徽境内著名人物</caption><tr data-id="godpckyiqb"><th align="center" width="72" data-id="godpckyis7"><div class="para <a name="14" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_14" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="荣誉称号" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2  J-chapter " data-index="14" data-uuid="godq6602l3" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>荣誉称号</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="14" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="audio-play part-audio-play J-part-audio-play" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_voice-play"></em>
<span class="J-part-audio-text">播报</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq6bpueu" >2020年12月25日，被国家卫生健康委等授予“<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%97%A0%E5%81%BF%E7%8C%AE%E8%A1%80%E5%85%88%E8%BF%9B%E7%9C%81%EF%BC%88%E5%B8%82%EF%BC%89%E5%A5%96/62681058" data-lemmaid="62681058">无偿献血先进省（市）奖</a>”。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="43" data-ctrmap=":43,">
[43]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_43_27969" id="ref_43_27969">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="sYCHrP5kIFDE" >2021年1月，入选2020年水利建设拟激励省份名单。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="57" data-ctrmap=":57,">
[57]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_57_27969" id="ref_57_27969">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="sKEfulOhbiVK" >2021年9月，国家智能社会治理实验基地名单公布，安徽省入选特色基地（环境治理、卫生健康）。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="49" data-ctrmap=":49,">
[49]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_49_27969" id="ref_49_27969">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="sTIVmE95b2Xl" >2022年，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%86%9C%E4%B8%9A%E5%86%9C%E6%9D%91%E9%83%A8/22429516" data-lemmaid="22429516">农业农村部</a>、国家发展改革委、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%95%86%E5%8A%A1%E9%83%A8/1251025" data-lemmaid="1251025">商务部</a>等部门认定新一批413家企业为农业产业化国家重点龙头企业，其中安徽省有21家企业入围，总数达到83家，从全国第10位跃居第6位。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="52" data-ctrmap=":52,">
[52]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_52_27969" id="ref_52_27969">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="sYCJXRQhOWhR" >2022年2月，入选2021年水利建设督查激励省份名单。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="58" data-ctrmap=":58,">
[58]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_58_27969" id="ref_58_27969">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list  MARK_MODULE">
<a name="15" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub27969_15" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="对外交往" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2  J-chapter " data-index="15" data-uuid="tySZm21bZuTu" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">安徽省</span>对外交往</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="15" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="audio-play part-audio-play J-part-audio-play" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_voice-play"></em>
<span class="J-part-audio-text">播报</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="para MARK_MODULE" label-module="para" data-uuid="godq56qpvs" >截至2017年9月，安徽省与美国<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%A9%AC%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B0%E5%B7%9E/3438236" data-lemmaid="3438236">马里兰州</a>、韩国<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B1%9F%E5%8E%9F%E9%81%93/5158717" data-lemmaid="5158717">江原道</a>、白俄罗斯<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B8%83%E5%88%97%E6%96%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%B7%9E/8325736" data-lemmaid="8325736">布列斯特州</a>缔结为姐妹省州、友好省道、友好省州，安徽省友城关系总数达78对，同时与140多个国家和地区建立了多种联系，与外国150多个科研院所、产品研发和培训机构、各类学校等开展了各种形式的合作，与外国70多个友好组织建立了交往关系，与<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%9C%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9A/390261" data-lemmaid="390261">东南亚</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2/200267" data-lemmaid="200267">美洲</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2/145550" data-lemmaid="145550">欧洲</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B4%8B%E6%B4%B2/195695" data-lemmaid="195695">大洋洲</a>的近200个华侨华人社团组织及500多位侨界知名人士建立了联系。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="21-22" data-ctrmap=":21,:22,">
[21-22]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_21_27969" id="ref_21_27969">&nbsp;</a><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_22_27969" id="ref_22_27969">&nbsp;</a></div><table log-set-param="table_view" <ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-issueId="8983237">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=1740794e607654704de2f294&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" class="cover" target="_blank">
<div class="cover-mask J-cover-mask" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/08f790529822720e0cf36338099b1d46f21fbf097dea?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_d2F0ZXIvYmFpa2UxNTA=,g_7,xp_5,yp_5)">
</div>
</a>
<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=1740794e607654704de2f294&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines">阜阳之战，2万南宋军大胜10万金军</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
安徽省是出了名的农业大省，而阜阳市又是安徽省出了名的农业大市。过去提到阜阳，主要是农业出名，九十年代以后，阜阳成为华东地区重要的交通枢纽之一，漯（河）阜铁路、阜淮（南）铁路、青（淮北青龙山）阜铁路以及作为南北铁路大动脉之一的京九铁路。另外，京港高铁也经阜阳，阜
</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="empty-box"></div>
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=0lg9h4a0HCwUZrUKnhkD6w&amp;authorId=&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area" style="background-image: url(https://gips0.baidu.com/it/u=1415105511,2492421574&amp;fm=3012&amp;app=3012&amp;autime=1683865328&amp;size=b200,200);">
<i class="bjh-author-type-1"></i></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<span>地图帝</span>
<span class="intro">优质历史领域创作者</span>
</div>
</a>
</div>
</li><li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-issueId="3575265">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=fa52d4632502e68f0d256a13&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" class="cover" target="_blank">
<div class="cover-mask J-cover-mask" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/faedab64034f78f0a98726ab76310a55b2191cdd?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_d2F0ZXIvYmFpa2UxMTY=,g_7,xp_5,yp_5)">
</div>
</a>
<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=fa52d4632502e68f0d256a13&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines">安徽省会为何要从长江边的安庆搬到合肥？</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
21世纪以来，安徽省会合肥经济不断蓬勃发展，经济总量逐步壮大，位列全国城市20位。而在1995年时，合肥仅排在100名。 随着经济的不断发展，合肥在安徽省内的经济地位，也由此日益突出。
</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="empty-box"></div>
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=9x3bjm6wGTONupfvWy-CzA&amp;authorId=&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/c8177f3e6709c93d5f52ba5f913df8dcd00054f1);">
</div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<span>环球情报员</span>
</div>
</a>
</div>
</li><li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-issueId="11666249">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=ced913fd4092c216c9380515&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" class="cover" target="_blank">
<div class="cover-mask J-cover-mask" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/314e251f95cad1c8a786c084e86d7009c93d70cffb4f?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_d2F0ZXIvYmFpa2UxMTY=,g_7,xp_5,yp_5)">
</div>
</a>
<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=ced913fd4092c216c9380515&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines">“散装”的安徽，到底什么味儿？</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
八大菜系中，安徽之所以有一席之地，是因为皖南美食的代表徽菜。就像“安徽”的徽得名一样，徽菜也是整个安徽美食在圈外的第一名片。
</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="empty-box"></div>
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=7t2oxJ0b9qjvKJnwCuYDBw&amp;authorId=&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area" style="background-image: url(https://gips0.baidu.com/it/u=394103379,1953119910&amp;fm=3012&amp;app=3012&amp;autime=1677754370&amp;size=b200,200);">
<i class="bjh-author-type-2"></i></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<span>地道风物</span>
<span class="intro">地道风物官方帐号</span>
</div>
</a>
</div>
</li><li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-issueId="338502">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=84a16c8985b84b4bf83ddeaf&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" class="cover" target="_blank">
<div class="filter-img" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/314e251f95cad1c847ef077b743e6709c93d5112?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_d2F0ZXIvYmFpa2U5Mg==,g_7,xp_5,yp_5)"></div>
<div class="cover-mask J-cover-mask vertical-img" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/314e251f95cad1c847ef077b743e6709c93d5112?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_d2F0ZXIvYmFpa2U5Mg==,g_7,xp_5,yp_5)">
</div>
</a>
<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=84a16c8985b84b4bf83ddeaf&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines">安徽为什么喜欢换省会？地球知识局</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
安徽的省会该怎么确定是个千古难题。人望最高的南京不在安徽，历史最久的安庆位置太偏，四通八达的合肥底蕴不够，还有一票皖东南的小兄弟虎视眈眈……
</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="empty-box"></div>
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=KRoxx7PUQ2Eiy-T8NmRO-w&amp;authorId=&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area" style="background-image: url(https://gips0.baidu.com/it/u=1349122658,2608679132&amp;fm=3012&amp;app=3012&amp;autime=1680602801&amp;size=b200,200);">
<i class="bjh-author-type-3"></i></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<span>地球知识局</span>
<span class="intro">优质国际领域创作者</span>
</div>
</a>
</div>
</li></ul>
</li>
<li class="slider-item">
<ul class="tashuo-list">
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-issueId="12362887">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=f483ebd1aefe40d63710c67b&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" class="cover" target="_blank">
<div class="cover-mask J-cover-mask" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/9a504fc2d5628535e5dd969a6dba61c6a7efce1bc548?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_d2F0ZXIvYmFpa2U5Mg==,g_7,xp_5,yp_5)">
</div>
</a>
<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=f483ebd1aefe40d63710c67b&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines">为什么说安徽和江苏是一对“双胞胎省”？江苏和安徽长得有多像？</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
中国的34个省级行政区中，有两个成员极为特殊：安徽和江苏——它们不仅紧紧依偎，而且有着接近的相貌。无论身世渊源、地貌水文、文化习俗，它们都仿佛对方的“镜像”，我们完全可以称呼它们为——中国的“双胞胎省”。
</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="empty-box"></div>
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=ag6SzzcqM5NPHgQ8a615hA&amp;authorId=&amp;from=lemma" target="_blank">

</li><li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-issueId="3819731">
<a href="/planet/issue?issueId=3819731&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" class="cover" target="_blank">
<div class="cover-mask J-cover-mask" style="background-image: url(https://bkimg.cdn.bcebos.com/pic/7af40ad162d9f2d3572cf7b28ea09d13632762d06613?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_d2F0ZXIvYmFpa2UxODA=,g_7,xp_5,yp_5)">
</div>
</a>
<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/planet/issue?issueId=3819731&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines"></p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
叶柄圆柱形，密生倒刺。花单生于花梗顶端、高托水面之上，有单瓣、复瓣、重瓣及重台等花型；花色有白、粉、深红、淡紫色或间色等变化；花期6～9月，每日晨开暮闭。果熟期9～10月。 莲花（学名：Nelumbo
</p>
</a>

<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=cf48fae33149adc0630f30d4&amp;lemmaId=526353&amp;fromLemmaModule=pcBottom&amp;lemmaTitle=安徽省&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines">若安庆省会地位没被合肥夺走，现在会怎样？</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
从清朝康熙六年（1667 年）设安徽省起，安庆做了270年的安徽省省会，安徽省的得名也是取自安庆的“安”和徽州的“徽”，后来安庆省会的地位被合肥夺了去。假若安徽省的省会依然在安庆，现在会是个什么样的情况呢？
</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="empty-box"></div>

<span>地图帝</span>
<span class="intro">优质历史领域创作者</span>
</div>
</a>

<p class="title two-lines">一到秋天，安徽就变成了徽州</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
登黄山之巅，俯瞰秋日美景 。 漫步古乡间，搜寻内心宁静 。 看文化遗迹，品读千年历史 。 尝百种风味，感受地方特色。

<p class="title two-lines">上保河南下保江苏，一年又一年隐身在洪水背后的安徽人</p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
“河南洪水主要流向安徽，目前来看对安徽的影响暂时不大，后续要关注台风‘烟花’登陆后安徽降雨情况。”  “烟花”已经登陆，也就是说，今年的防汛挑战，对安徽而言，才刚刚开始。  在这里，我只希望今年泄洪的概率越小越好。
</p>
</a>

<div class="title-abstract">
<a href="/planet/issue?issueId=3817210&amp;fromModule=lemma_bottom-tashuo-article" target="_blank">
<p class="title two-lines"></p>
<p class="J-abstract abstract hidden">
牧羊归来 八公山峰峦叠翠，清泉密布，景色优美。 八公山的风力发电机一排排，很高大威武，风车钢塔直径约3米，高约40多米。 八公山,山势绵延，一脉四十峰，处处景致迷人,被誉为“八公仙境”、“峻极之山”。 八公山是一座历史文化名山，又名紫金山，由四十余座山峰叠嶂而
</p>
</a>
</div>

    var cookie = require('wiki-common:widget/util/cookie');
    if (!cookie.get('baikedeclare')) {
        $('#J-declare-wrap').css('display', 'block');

        clickstream.logViewEl({
            page: 'lemma',
            element: 'statement-top'
        });
    }
    $('#J-declare-close').on('click', function () {
        // 用户关闭后，不再显示，过期时间调整为90天
        cookie.set('baikedeclare', 'showed', {
            expires: 90 * 60 * 60 * 24 * 1000,
            path: '/'
        });
        $('#J-declare-wrap').css('display', 'none');
    });

    $('.declare-details').on('click', function () {
        clickstream.logActClick({
            page: 'lemma',
            element: 'statement-top'
        });
    });
}();
!function(){var cookie = require('wiki-common:widget/util/cookie');
var $ = require('wiki-common:widget/lib/jquery/jquery');
var clickstream = require('wiki-common:widget/tools/clickstream/clickstream');

var timer = '';
var requestTime= null;
var currentTime= new Date().getTime();
$('.wgt-navbar').on('mouseenter', 'dl', function() {
  clearTimeout(timer);
  timer = setTimeout(function() {
    $('.wgt-navbar').addClass('wgt-navbar-hover');
    clickstream.logActEvent({
      page: 'common',
      act_type: 'hover',
      element: 'navbar-hover'
    });
  }, 300);
}).on('mouseleave', function() {
  clearTimeout(timer);
  $('.wgt-navbar').removeClass('wgt-navbar-hover');
}).on('click', 'a', function() {
  clearTimeout(timer);
  $('.wgt-navbar').removeClass('wgt-navbar-hover');
});
// 30分钟后更新json文件参数，防止浏览器的缓存（仅用当前时间戳会导致带宽压力过大）
if (!cookie.get('zhishiTopicRequestTime') || (currentTime - cookie.get('zhishiTopicRequestTime') > 1800000)) {
  cookie.set('zhishiTopicRequestTime', currentTime);
  requestTime = currentTime;
} else {
  requestTime = cookie.get('zhishiTopicRequestTime');
}
$.getJSON('https://baikebcs.cdn.bcebos.com/cms/pc_index/knowledge_topic_menu.json?time='+ requestTime, function(data) {
    for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
        var url = data[i].itemId;
        if (url.indexOf('http') === -1) {
          url = "https://baike.baidu.com/wapui/subpage/knowledgetopic?id=" + url 
        }
        $('#J-knowledge-content').append('<div><a href="' + url + '" target="_blank">' + data[i].title + '</a></div>')
    }
})
}();
!function(){   var nslog = require('wiki-common:widget/component/nslog/nslog');
   nslog(10000105);
}();
!function(){    var $ = require('wiki-common:widget/lib/jquery/jquery');
    var rightCheck = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/rightCheck/rightCheck');
    var nsLog = require('wiki-common:widget/component/nslog/nslog');
    var Dialog = require("wiki-common:widget/ui/dialog/dialog");
    var clickstream = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/clickstream/clickstream');
    var EventHub = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/eventHub/eventHub.es');
    // 展现策略
    rightCheck.editView('526353', function(res) {
        if (!res.errno) {
            if (res.data.edit) {
                clickstream.logViewEl({
                    page: 'lemma',
                    element: 'edit_btn',
                });
                $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .edit-lemma').css('display', 'inline-block');
                EventHub.LemmaEvent.emit(EventHub.LEMMA_EVENTS.LEMMA_TITLE_EDIT_ICON_TOGGLE, true);
                // 编辑和申请本人实名验证保证同一行展示
                if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').length > 0) {
                  if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .edit-lemma').offset().left > $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').offset().left) {
                    $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .edit-lemma').before('<br/><br/>');
                  }
                }
            } else {
                nsLog('10003104');
                $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .lock-lemma').show();
                // 锁定和申请本人实名验证保证同一行展示
                if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').length > 0) {
                  if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .lock-lemma').offset().left > $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').offset().left) {
                    $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .lock-lemma').before('<br/><br/>');
                  }
                }
            }
        } else {
            if ('1') {
                clickstream.logViewEl({
                    page: 'lemma',
                    element: 'edit_btn',
                });
                $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .edit-lemma').css('display', 'inline-block');
                EventHub.LemmaEvent.emit(EventHub.LEMMA_EVENTS.LEMMA_TITLE_EDIT_ICON_TOGGLE, true);
                // 编辑和申请本人实名验证保证同一行展示
                if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').length > 0) {
                  if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .edit-lemma').offset().left > $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').offset().left) {
                    $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .edit-lemma').before('<br/><br/>');
                  }
                }
            } else {
                nsLog('10003104');
                $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .lock-lemma').show();
                // 锁定和申请本人实名验证保证同一行展示
                if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').length > 0) {
                  if ($('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .lock-lemma').offset().left > $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .personal').offset().left) {
                    $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .lock-lemma').before('<br/><br/>');
                  }
                }
            }
        }
    });

    var canDiscussion = $('.j-discussion-link').length > 0 ? true : false;
    if (canDiscussion) {
        var discussionKey = 'discussion' + 526353;
        var discussionNum = 0;
        var content = '<div style="text-align: left;width: 528px">'
            + '<h2 style="font-size: 20px;color: #333;line-height: 26px;margin-bottom: 20px;">'
            + '词条锁定，暂时无法编辑</h2>'
            + '<p style="font-size: 16px;color: #333;line-height: 26px;">'
            + '亲爱的用户，词条存在争议或词条内容较完善都可能被锁定（'
            + '<a href="/view/10812319.htm" target="_blank">查看详情</a>）。</p>'
            + '<p style="font-size: 16px;color: #333;line-height: 26px;">'
            + '如果你认为锁定词条内容存在问题需要修改，可进行以下操作：</p></div>';
        var noFlashDialog = new Dialog({
            title: '编辑提示',
            content: content,
            btns: [
                {
                    text: '<span style="font-size: 14px">参与词条讨论，反馈词条问题</span>',
                    key: 'discussion'
                }
            ],
            onBtnClick: function(btnKey){
                if (btnKey === 'discussion') {
                    setTimeout(function() {
                        window.open(window.location.origin + '/planet/talk?lemmaId=526353&category=1');
                    }, 300);
                }
            },
        })
        // 锁定跳转
        $('body').on('click', '.lock-lemma', function () {
            var me = $(this);
            noFlashDialog.show();
        });
        // 获取讨论数
        $.get('/discussion/api/getdiscussioncount?lemmaId=526353', function (res) {
            if (res && res.errno === 0 && res.data.discussionCount > 0) {
                var lastNum = parseInt(localStorage.getItem(discussionKey)) || 0;
                discussionNum = res.data.discussionCount;
                var numText = (res.data.discussionCount - lastNum) <= 99 ? (res.data.discussionCount - lastNum) : '99+';
                if (numText > 0 || numText === '99+') {
                    $('.j-discussion-link .num').text(numText).show();
                }

            }
        });
        $('.lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle .j-discussion-link').on('click', function () {
            localStorage.setItem(discussionKey, discussionNum);
            $(this).find('.num').remove();
        });
        // 讨论按钮展现量
        nsLog(90000101, window.location.href, {
            lemmaid: 526353
        });
    }
    // 他说讨论入口展现打点
    function showTashuoDiscussion() {
        var discussion = $('.j-discussion-link[nslog-type="90000102"]');
        var jVars = $('#J-vars');
        if (discussion.length === 1) {
            var logParam = {
                page: 'lemma',
                element: 'tashuo-issue-list-entrance',
                lemmaId: jVars.attr('data-lemmaid'),
                lemmaTitle: jVars.attr('data-lemmatitle')
            };
            clickstream.logViewEl(logParam);
        }
    }
    
    // 他说讨论入口点击打点
    function clickTashuoDiscussion() {
        var discussion = $('.j-discussion-link[nslog-type="90000102"]');
        var jVars = $('#J-vars');
        if (discussion.length === 1) {
            discussion.on('click', function() {
                var logParam = {
                    page: 'lemma',
                    element: 'tashuo-issue-list-entrance',
                    lemmaId: jVars.attr('data-lemmaid'),
                    lemmaTitle: jVars.attr('data-lemmatitle')
                };
                clickstream.logActClick(logParam);
            })
           
        }
    }
    showTashuoDiscussion();
    clickTashuoDiscussion();
}();
!function(){    var $ = require('wiki-common:widget/lib/jquery/jquery');
    var nsLog = require('wiki-common:widget/component/nslog/nslog');
    var clickstream = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/clickstream/clickstream');
    lemmaId = 526353;
    lemmaTitle='安徽省';
    var lemmaDesc = "\u4e2d\u534e\u4eba\u6c11\u5171\u548c\u56fd\u7701\u7ea7\u884c\u653f\u533a";

    var logMap ={
        uploadShow: 10800000,
        uploadClick: 10800001
    };
    nsLog(logMap.uploadShow, window.location.href, {
        lemmaid: lemmaId,
        lemmaTitle: lemmaTitle
    });

    function gotoPage(url, id) {
        var el = document.createElement('a');

        el.setAttribute('href', encodeURI(url));
        el.setAttribute('target', '_blank');
        el.setAttribute('id', id);

        if(!document.getElementById(id)) {
            document.body.appendChild(el);
        }

        el.click();
    }

    $('.J-add-video-link').on('click', function() {
        var videoLocation = '';
        if ($('.J-second-normal').length) {
            videoLocation = 'top-common';
        }
        else if ($('.large-feature').length) {
            videoLocation = 'top-large-feature';
        }
        else if ($('.J-related-video-container').length) {
            videoLocation = 'lemma-video';
        }
        clickstream.logActClick({
            page: 'lemma',
            element: 'video-upload',
            type: 1,
            location: 0,
            lemmaTitle: lemmaTitle,
            lemmaId: lemmaId,
            videoLocation: videoLocation
        });
        nsLog(logMap.uploadClick, window.location.href, {
            lemmaid: lemmaId,
            lemmaTitle: lemmaTitle
        });
        var url = '/second/publish?lemmaId=' + lemmaId + '&from=lemma&lemmaTitle=' + lemmaTitle + '&lemmaDesc=' + lemmaDesc;

        gotoPage(url, 'a_blank_tag')
    })
}();
!function(){    var $ = require('wiki-common:widget/lib/jquery/jquery');
    var userLogin = require('wiki-common:widget/component/userLogin/userLogin');

    var $loftEditBtn = $('#J-special-edit');
    var lemmaId = 526353;

    var loftEditUrl = '/editor/load/loftload?lemmaId=' +  lemmaId;

    // 获取 loft 的编辑权限
    function getLoftEditPrivilege() {
        return $.ajax({
            type: 'GET',
            url: '/editor/check/getlofteditprivilege',
            dataType: 'JSON'
        });
    }

    userLogin.checkIfLogin({
        ifMsg: true,
        // 已登录状态
        onLogin: function (res) {
            getLoftEditPrivilege().then(function(res) {
                $loftEditBtn.css(
                    'display',
                    res.data && res.data.length ? 'inline-block' : 'none'
                );
            });
        },
        onUnlogin: function () {
            $loftEditBtn.css('display', 'none');
        }
    });

    $loftEditBtn.on('click', function() {
        userLogin.checkIfLogin({
            ifMsg: true,
            // 已登录状态
            onLogin: function (res) {
                if (res.errno === 0) {
                    window.location.href = loftEditUrl;
                }
            },
            onUnlogin: function () {
                userLogin.showLoginPop();
            }
        });
    });

}();

!function(){    var $ = require('wiki-common:widget/lib/jquery/jquery');
    var Dialog = require("wiki-common:widget/ui/dialog/dialog");
    var userLogin = require('wiki-common:widget/component/userLogin/userLogin');
    var unameFiller = require('wiki-common:widget/component/unameFiller/unameFiller');
    var rightCheck = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/rightCheck/rightCheck');
    var checkUgc = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/rightCheck/checkUgc');
    var nsLog = require('wiki-common:widget/component/nslog/nslog');
    var clickstream = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/clickstream/clickstream');
    var jumpLink = require('wiki-common:packages/utils/jumpLink');

            var isEnterprise = false;
        var enterpriseOwnerUserId = 0;
    
    var userId = 0;
    var editUrl = '/editor/load/editload?lemmaTitle=' + encodeURIComponent('安徽省') + '&lemmaId=' + '526353';
    var pgcUrl = '/enterprise/editpgc?lemmaId=526353';

    userLogin.regist({
        onLogin: function(user) {
            userId = user ? user.uid : 0;
        }
    });

    function showChoseEditDialog(pgcCallback, ugcCallback) {
        new Dialog({
            title: '编辑提示',
            subMsg: '<p>您已开通企业百科服务，推荐您直接编辑“官方资料”，官方资料仅限企业百科绑定的百科账号修改，其他用户账号不可修改。</p><p>如果您想修改其他网友编辑的普通词条内容，请注意遵守百科百科编辑规则。<p>',
            btns: [{
            key: 'pgc',
            text: '编辑官方资料'
            }, {
            style: 'white',
            text: '修改普通词条',
            key: 'ugc'
            }],
            onBtnClick: function(btnKey){
                if (btnKey === 'pgc') {
                    pgcCallback && pgcCallback();
                } else if (btnKey === 'ugc') {
                    ugcCallback && ugcCallback();
                }
            }
        }).show();
    }

    function checkUserLegal(res) {
        var legal = false;
        switch (res.errno) {
            case 100001:
                nsLog('10003106');
                userLogin.showLoginPop();
                break;
            case 100006:
                unameFiller.show();
                break;
            default:
                legal = true;
        }
        return legal;
    }

    $(document.body).on('click', '.j-edit-link', function () {
        nsLog('10003100');
        var dl = $(this).attr('data-edit-dl');
        var entry = $(this).attr('data-entry');
        if (dl) {
            var url = editUrl + '&ci=' + dl;
        } else {
            var url = editUrl;
        }

        rightCheck.preeditCheck(
            {
                lemmaId: '526353',
                lemmaTitle: '安徽省',
                lemmaDesc: '中华人民共和国省级行政区',
                versionId: '511303553',
                action: '',
                ci: dl
            },
            function (res) {
                if (!checkUserLegal(res)) {
                    return;
                }
                if (entry) {
                    var entryString = '&entry=' + entry;
                    url += entryString;
                    pgcUrl += entryString;
                }
                if (isEnterprise && enterpriseOwnerUserId === userId) {
                    showChoseEditDialog(
                        function () {
                            jumpLink(pgcUrl);
                        },
                        function () {
                            checkUgc(res, '526353', url);
                        }
                    );
                } else {
                    checkUgc(res, '526353', url);
                }
            }
        );
    });
}();

!function(){    var $ = require('wiki-common:widget/lib/jquery/jquery'),
      animation = require('wiki-common:widget/util/animation'),
      nslog = require('wiki-common:widget/component/nslog/nslog'),
      initSearchbar = require('wiki-common:widget/component/searchbar/searchbar');
    var isFadeIn = false,
        isFadeOut = false;
    var clickstream = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/clickstream/clickstream');
    var logUtils = require('wiki-lemma:widget/tools/logUtils/logUtils.es');
    var fadeInAni, fadeOutAni;
    var isShowLog = false;
    $(window).on('scroll', function(e) {
        var scrollTop = $(this).scrollTop();
        if (scrollTop > 200 && !isFadeIn && $('.lemmaWgt-searchHeader').css('display') == 'none') {
            if (!isShowLog) {
                logUtils.logViewEl('top-search-bar');
            }
            fadeOutAni && fadeOutAni.stop();
            fadeInAni = animation({
                duration: 200,
                easing: 'linear',
                onStart: function() {
                    isFadeOut = false;
                    isFadeIn = true;
                    $('.lemmaWgt-searchHeader').css('display', 'block');
                },
                onStep: function(progress) {
                    $('.lemmaWgt-searchHeader').css('opacity', progress)
                },
                onComplete: function(progress) {
                    isFadeIn = false;
                    nslog(10010007);
                    clickstream.logViewEl({
                        page: 'lemma',
                        element: 'topbar_edit'
                    });
                    clickstream.logViewEl({
                        page: 'lemma',
                        element: 'topbar_discussion'
                    });
                }
            });
        } else if (scrollTop <= 200 && !isFadeOut && $('.lemmaWgt-searchHeader').css('display') == 'block') {
            fadeInAni && fadeInAni.stop();
            fadeOutAni = animation({
                duration: 300,
                easing: 'linear',
                onStart: function() {
                    $('.lemmaWgt-searchHeader #suggestion').hide();
                    isFadeIn = false;
                    isFadeOut = true;
                },
                onStep: function(progress) {
                    $('.lemmaWgt-searchHeader').css('opacity', 1 - progress);
                },
                onComplete: function(progress) {
                    isFadeOut = false;
                    $('.lemmaWgt-searchHeader').css('display', 'none');
                }
            });
        }
    });
}();
